      "span_text": "To further substantiate the involvement of 5-LO in the dexamethasone-dependent effect on Ab formation, we next used MEFs isolated from transgenic mice over-expressing the Swedish APP mutant (i.e., Tg2576), or Tg2576 genetically deficient for 5-LO (Tg2576/5-LO 2/2 )"
